<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN272">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>maṇituṇarn taṉṉa mākkura ṉocci</l>
<l>pōtuviri palmara ṉuḷḷuñ ciṟanta</l>
<l>kāta ṉaṉmara nīniḻaṟ ṟiciṉē</l>
<l>kaṭiyuṭai viyaṉakark kāṇvarap polinta</l>
<l>toṭiyuṭai makaḷi ralkuluṅ kiṭatti</l>
<l>kāppuṭaip puricai pukkumā ṟaḻittali</l>
<l>ṉūrppuṟaṅ koṭāa neṭuntakai</l>
<l>pīṭukeḻu ceṉṉik kiḻamaiyu niṉatē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Nocci with dark [flower] ears, as if sapphires were clustering,</l>
<l>you beloved good tree that is superior even among many trees </l>
<l>expanding [their] buds, may you give shade!</l>
<l>You will lie on the hips of bangled women</l>
<l>who visibly flourish in protected wide mansions,</l>
<l>and your’s too is the mastery over the great head</l>
<l>of the paragon who did not flee the village</l>
<l>because [the enemy] entered the guarded fortification [and] destroyed the opposition.  </l>
</lg>
    </div>
